headline: Clorox (CLX): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q1 Earnings?
summary: Clorox’s stock price has taken a beating over the past six months, shedding 21.7% of its value and falling to $130.88 per share. This was partly due to its softer quarterly results and may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
